structure.unit: B FERTILIZER AND PESTICIDE USE AND APPLICATION

law.text: This chapter shall be known as the "Kentucky Fertilizer and Pesticide Storage, and Pesticide Use and Application Act of 1996."
law.history: Amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 171, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1996. -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 1.
